{"tid":1644582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有人同我聽住，一定要幫女學生討回公道。","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:32:17.000Z","uid":220066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77bc727f8f0c22eadf47644ede757f4b708576d9","tid":1644582,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"首先，段崇知我屌你老母祖宗十八代<br />\n身為中文大學校長連保護學生都唔敢去保護<br />\n而且唔敢去譴責黑警暴力，好明顯避得就避<br />\n<br />\n而家女學生人身安全一定受到好大威脅<br />\n唔該將呢單野話比所羅門聽<br />\n一定要上國際新聞話比全世界人聽<br />\n加上呢個女仔一定要受到保護<br />\n同埋最好移民去美國受到應有保護<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府同黑警有幾咁仆街<br />\n而家大家休息完未，仲有無籍口比自己害怕極權政府<br />\n大家係時係要企出來反抗<br />\n<br />\n如果唔反抗既話，香港一定輸撚緊<br />\n你地班人甘心會打輸場將？<br />\n<br />\n好好反省下啦"},{"pid":"9a1d6788bb4a03fa06de53398bc9fa689a180c0f","tid":1644582,"uid":135503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gz0p5Y-AUjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGz0p5Y-AUjE&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5W58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=1b6b6075\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gz0p5Y-AUjE</a><br />\nbackup"},{"pid":"977a028dd352b5a98736475ed278a600651937ba","tid":1644582,"uid":163943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0661b91a74f2f52fdd01f8ed2c2f84e4cf2f51e9","tid":1644582,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46a1edfe38e72e3f2b9afa18e5075f7f844681fb","tid":1644582,"uid":249041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}